{"type":null,"faqId":49520,"title":"使用世界时钟","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"世界时钟\"XE \"添加城市\"XE \"设置时区\"XE \"删除城市\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189838\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“时钟”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在“时钟”页签下，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>添加城市：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189839\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，输入城市名称，或从城市列表中选择城市。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>设置时区：点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189840\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，设置家中的时区以及系统日期和时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>删除城市：点击“编辑城市”，点击要删除城市旁边的“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189841\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，然后点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189842\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1094,"faqType":"生活助手","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5264","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Convenient-features","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294498000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":22,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}